{"tid":213150,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[sci jj 福音] 人工低無專業唔緊要，即刻番個醫務化驗師牌就得","createTime":"2017-04-23T03:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T09:56:11.000Z","uid":38089,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2283c7f2433f16292cae1ff446a2b093d1d7ee4e","tid":213150,"uid":38089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:02:48.000Z","msg":"相信各位sci fresh grad都開始搵緊工啦，有無發現大部既工都係人工低，工時長仲要好似唔憂請人呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實sci fac根本就係一個騙局，如果你唔係做到教師或者研究生，你既人工都肯定係全大學所有fresh grad裏面最低既。<br />\n<br />\n係香港生活，又要養家，又要出街同朋友social下，其實萬幾蚊邊夠使？我明，我真係明。因為我以前都係咁。不過唔使驚，我開post就係想話比大家聽你係有能力改變現狀既。只要你係<br />\n1.biological related sci degree holder<br />\n2.個人夠勤力<br />\n3.有心為左長遠既career捱幾個月<br />\n<br />\n你就可以報考MLT。MLT HA入職人工有20k，升到盡有3&times;k。<br />\n詳情可以睇fb page，聯絡fb版主 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/mltexam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fmltexam&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ec91b073\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/mltexam</a><br />\n或者email: mltonetakepass@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n希望大家都可以搵多D!"},{"pid":"bf78ba736d6648882ee21969bd92b5be4749ab2d","tid":213150,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"留名等睇俾連登捧到爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f888848f427859d646551590eb46e7ec65316d","tid":213150,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"咁你考完牌搵到工未先"},{"pid":"83fe7df436926180be17b639bdf25ad1dba91609","tid":213150,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"又係開班狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6193d25e9fc2864fe18f2c090ffd5603eac14dc","tid":213150,"uid":31254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:22:46.000Z","msg":"爆喇屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 